你们必须现在就问自己

505
00:31:54,960 --> 00:31:59,160
"what kind of life do I want for myself?"
"我到底想要什么样的生活"

506
00:32:01,490 --> 00:32:02,950
I gave an example of business.
我给的是一个生意场上的例子

507
00:32:03,170 --> 00:32:07,030
It applies as much to any other domain-
其实对于其他领域也一样

508
00:32:07,280 --> 00:32:12,000
whether you are,want to become a medical doctor
不管你是想成为一个医生

509
00:32:12,780 --> 00:32:15,610
and going on and feeling pressure to get into the best schools,
是因为能否上到最好的学校而有压力

510
00:32:15,800 --> 00:32:18,110
the best department,the best internship,
是想要最好的公寓 最好的实习机会

511
00:32:18,330 --> 00:32:21,550
the best,the highest position and on and on;
最想要好的 最高的职位等等

512
00:32:22,550 --> 00:32:27,040
or whether you are working for a non profit organization;
或者你是打算为非盈利机构工作

513
00:32:27,390 --> 00:32:32,020
or whether you are in academia; or a lawyer.
无论你是留在学术界 还是成为律师

514
00:32:32,230 --> 00:32:38,670
It doesn't matter- just filling the blank of Mr X in which area.
都一样 都是在不同领域重复X先生的故事

515
00:32:38,900 --> 00:32:40,790
It applies to any place.
这样的情况适用于任何地方

516
00:32:41,770 --> 00:32:45,930
And the question is,"what kind of life do I want for myself?"
问题就是 "我们想要什么样的生活"

517
00:32:46,150 --> 00:32:47,540
And remember the most important thing,
要记住其中最重要的

518
00:32:47,740 --> 00:32:49,360
a person committed to excellence
一个追求卓越的人

519
00:32:49,590 --> 00:32:52,320
does not give up on being ambitious.
不会放弃自己的雄心

520
00:32:52,640 --> 00:32:54,730
However,a person committed to excellence
但是 一个追求卓越的人

521
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:59,200
does not also give up on the journey.
也不会放弃整个旅途

522
